void matchesWithLogicalAnd(){
    stubFor(
        post("/date")
            .withRequestBody(
                matchingJsonPath(
                    "$.date", after("2020-05-01T00:00:00Z").and(before("2021-05-01T00:00:00Z"))))
            .willReturn(ok()));

    assertThat(
        testClient
            .postJson("/date", "{\n" + "  \"date\": \"2020-12-31T00:00:00Z\"\n" + "}")
            .statusCode(),
        is(200));

    assertThat(
        testClient
            .postJson("/date", "{\n" + "  \"date\": \"2011-12-31T00:00:00Z\"\n" + "}")
            .statusCode(),
        is(404));
  }
